parameters: \nw[Thief 2]Good, I'll ram it straight into your throat!

\nw[Nonna]I understand how you feel, but if you want to help
her, you need to stay calm.

\nw[Kuno]U-uh... Y-yeah, you're right. I understand, I'll
do my best.

\nw[Kuno]If we're going to launch a surprise attack, now is
the chance, right? Everyone is focused on her, and
it seems like they're not paying attention to us.

\nw[Nonna]I see, leave the rescue of her to me. I have a
plan.

\nw[Kuno]Understood. First, let's prepare. Once we're
ready, we'll storm in, subdue them, and rescue
her.
\nw[Nonna]Yes, I understand. Let's prepare for now.

\nw[Thief 1]Wha... an enemy attack!? What the hell were you
doing on watch duty!?

\nw[Nonna]Unfortunately, you'll be sleeping. I'll have you
all sleep here too.

\nw[Thief 1]Tch, no choice. There's nowhere to run, so I'll
take you down!

\nw[Nonna]Um, we are mercenaries. We received a request and
came here to exterminate the thieves.

\nw[Nonna]I will take care of this child, so could the two
of you restrain the incapacitated thieves and
contact the soldiers?
\nw[Kuno]I understand. Taro, leave it to me.

We restrained the thieves, carried them outside,
and contacted the soldiers to take them away.

\nw[Taro]Whew... That was close... They weren't very
strong, so I need to fight properly next time.
